akka.util

Class ImmutableIntMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.util.ImmutableIntMap

  • public final class ImmutableIntMap
extends java.lang.Object
    INTERNAL API Specialized Map for primitive Int keys and values to avoid allocations (boxing). Keys and values are encoded consecutively in a single Int array and does copy-on-write with no structural sharing, it's intended for rather small maps (<1000 elements).
